=begin pod
=TITLE Gnome::Gtk4::Spinner
=head1 Description

A B<Gnome::Gtk4::Spinner> widget displays an icon-size spinning animation.

It is often used as an alternative to a L<Gnome::Gtk4::ProgressBar|/content-docs/api2/reference/Gtk4/ProgressBar>
for displaying indefinite activity, instead of actual progress.

=for image :src<asset_files/images/spinner.png> :width<30%> :class<inline>

To start the animation, use L<.start()|#start>, to stop it
use L<.stop()|#stop>.

=head2 CSS nodes

B<Gnome::Gtk4::Spinner> has a single CSS node with the name spinner.
When the animation is active, the :checked pseudoclass is
added to this node.

